      "content": "it's just everything. the pain, the cold, the feeling that i'm just a burden to you because i can't even stand up anymore. it feels like there's no point in even trying to fix the wound. like why bother when everything is just falling apart anyway? it would be so much quieter if i could just... stop. if i could just let everything go. do you even think there's a reason to keep going like this?",
